lead_paragraph: Chinese retailer Suning Commerce Group is close to buying a leading stake in top-flight Italian soccer club Inter Milan, with a deal expected as early as this weekend, two sources said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: China's Suning Close to Buying Top Stake in Inter Milan-Sources
